Agapsys JDBC Tools
============================

Welcome to the JDBC Tools project.

Attention: If you obtained the source from a 'snapshot' branch be aware that 
such branch can contain unstable code.

Compiling
---------

The first build may take a long time as Maven downloads all the
dependencies.

Dependencies
------------

JDBC Tools project requires Java 7 compatible runtime and depends on the
following external libraries:

* Apache Commons DBCP

(for detailed information on external dependencies please see pom.xml)

Licensing
